        <guid>https://JaeKimdev.github.io/p/auto-layout2/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dwrejmale/image/upload/v1658929900/swift_dpaoqx.png" alt="Featured image of post Auto Layout(2)" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Auto Layout Guide에서 제공하는 Auto Layout CookBook 따라해보기&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;simple-constraints&#34;&gt;Simple Constraints&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;single-view&#34;&gt;Single View&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 5
